## Proxmox host configuration, storage, networking

## Hardware
- I7
- 16GB RAM (upgrading to 32-64GB planned)
- 2TB storage SSD

## Planned VMs on This Node
- DCO1 Domain Controller (AD DS, DNS)
- ADMIN01 (Adnin / Jumpbox)
- UTIL01 (Linux Utility Server)
- WSUS01 (Patch Management)
- Security Onion
- MAILDMZ (Email server in the DMZ)
- AZ-CONNECT (Azure AD Connect)

## What I've Learned So Far
- Understanding how proxmox storage pools work
- Basics of brides and how they map to physical NICs
- How to size VM CPU/RAM based on role



